      "width": 720,
      "height": 160,
      "color": "6",
      "text": "## ⚡ Runtime pipeline (отработка)\n\n1. **Open Folder** → lastWorkspace + path sandbox\n2. **indexWorkspace** (ast-graph) → fileCount\n3. **Session load cache?** → semantic-map.canvas\n4. else **contextPacker** → **LLM** (Mock | Haiku localhost) → **buildSemanticMap**\n5. **serializeDocument** → cache + **CanvasView.loadData**\n6. Click node → RIGHT content (text/summary/anchors)\n7. **Regenerate** force=true → rebuild map"
    },

